- An artist directory is available at `ArtistPage.tsx`, showing artists filterable by category.
- `ArtistDetailPage.tsx` shows details for a specific artist.
- Admin management for artists is in `pages/admin/Artists.tsx`.
- Admin management for artist categories is in `pages/admin/ArtistCategories.tsx`.

- Artist and artist category data is managed by `@services/artistService.ts` and `@services/artistCategoryService.ts` respectively.